&gt; &gt; is almost there, and all you should need to do is put @Inherited at the
&gt; &gt; beginning. So something like this is in order:
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; @Inherited // &lt;--- add this
&gt; &gt; @Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
&gt; &gt; @Target(ElementType.TYPE)
&gt; &gt; public static @interface Suite.SuiteClasses{ //rock on...
